WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'iTrix' is a Workbench game where you have to moves tiles with
various shapes, in a triangular board. As tiles of the same type
are placed next and linked to each other, they are then removed...
along with the link that connect each other...!

  The game is based on the average "sliding-tiles-on-a-board"
pattern of play, as a tile can only move if there's an empty space
next to it and, of course, if there is a link between that tile
and the empty space...

  One important thing to remember: do not isolate tiles on
impossible to reach areas...

  If you get stuck on one game board, or you want to restart a
game board, just click on the 'Restart' button. However, the
number of moves you have made on that board will accumulate until
you complete the board.

  When you complete a game board, iTrix displays a new board and
the game continues...

  Have fun!

